WEBVTT

1
00:02:29.550 --> 00:02:31.467
Up! Up!

2
00:02:41.592 --> 00:02:43.467
Hurry!

3
00:02:49.550 --> 00:02:51.467
Don't push!

4
00:02:56.550 --> 00:02:58.467
Hurry!

5
00:03:06.550 --> 00:03:08.425
Up the tree. quickly!

6
00:03:11.508 --> 00:03:15.425
Pull him down quickly. quickly!

7
00:03:17.550 --> 00:03:19.467
Catch the flag.

8
00:03:20.550 --> 00:03:22.508
Wait.

9
00:03:31.592 --> 00:03:33.467
Don't let him get down

10
00:03:46.550 --> 00:03:48.467
Hurry!

11
00:04:04.550 --> 00:04:06.467
Careful!

12
00:04:31.550 --> 00:04:33.467
Calm down! The winner this year...

13
00:04:34.550 --> 00:04:38.467
is Ai Bak Tim

14
00:04:49.550 --> 00:04:51.508
Sawadee everyone...

15
00:04:51.508 --> 00:04:53.550
from Ban Nong Pradoo.

16
00:04:53.550 --> 00:04:55.550
We are gathering for good merit at this festival.

17
00:04:55.550 --> 00:04:59.550
to give robes to the monks. and Ong Bak.

18
00:04:59.550 --> 00:05:03.550
who is the protective icon
for the well-being of our village.

19
00:05:03.550 --> 00:05:05.550
This festival...

20
00:05:05.550 --> 00:05:07.550
is to remind us that...

21
00:05:07.550 --> 00:05:09.550
in 7 days we will be...

22
00:05:09.550 --> 00:05:11.842
celebrating Ong Bak.

23
00:05:12.550 --> 00:05:14.508
The last time...

24
00:05:14.508 --> 00:05:18.425
being 24 years ago.

25
00:05:19.508 --> 00:05:21.508
This means...

26
00:05:21.508 --> 00:05:25.467
all prosperity will return to us once more.

27
00:05:35.592 --> 00:05:37.467
Where is the amulet?

28
00:05:42.550 --> 00:05:44.508
It's not good.

29
00:05:44.508 --> 00:05:46.550
There is a little damage -

30
00:05:46.550 --> 00:05:48.550
Not quite perfect.

31
00:05:48.550 --> 00:05:51.550
200.000 baht for this is not cheap.

32
00:05:51.550 --> 00:05:55.467
Why don't you want to sell it?

33
00:05:56.550 --> 00:05:59.550
Ow! How much do you want?

34
00:05:59.550 --> 00:06:02.550
Don. I'm not selling.

35
00:06:02.550 --> 00:06:05.508
Ow! Why do you change your mind?

36
00:06:05.508 --> 00:06:08.508
I came a long way from Bangkok just for this.

37
00:06:08.508 --> 00:06:10.550
I've never given you any promise...

38
00:06:10.550 --> 00:06:12.550
to sell it to you.

39
00:06:12.550 --> 00:06:14.550
I want to give this to my son. Bak Hum Lae.

40
00:06:14.550 --> 00:06:18.467
the day he's ordained here as a monk. for Ong Bak.

41
00:06:20.550 --> 00:06:24.592
Call me whenever you want to sell it.

42
00:06:24.592 --> 00:06:27.592
No. no. I don't have a telephone.

43
00:06:27.592 --> 00:06:29.550
I'll give you my address.

44
00:06:29.550 --> 00:06:31.550
so whenever you want to sell.

45
00:06:31.550 --> 00:06:33.508
you can write to me.

46
00:06:44.550 --> 00:06:46.550
Is this good enough. grandma?

47
00:06:46.550 --> 00:06:49.550
I made it for Ai Tim for his ordination.

48
00:06:49.550 --> 00:06:51.550
It's good.

49
00:06:51.550 --> 00:06:54.550
Where did Ai Tim come from.

50
00:06:54.550 --> 00:06:56.550
and how come he grew up in the temple?

51
00:06:56.550 --> 00:06:58.550
He's now a man.

52
00:06:58.550 --> 00:07:02.550
Ai Tim is an ophan.

53
00:07:02.550 --> 00:07:04.550
He was left at the temple by someone...

54
00:07:04.550 --> 00:07:06.550
when he was a baby.

55
00:07:06.550 --> 00:07:09.550
Pra Kroo (the Abbot) took pity on him.

56
00:07:09.550 --> 00:07:11.467
and adopted him.

57
00:07:12.550 --> 00:07:14.550
And everyone says...

58
00:07:14.550 --> 00:07:18.467
he has grown up well under Ong Bak.

59
00:07:25.550 --> 00:07:27.550
Hitting the earth!

60
00:07:27.550 --> 00:07:29.467
Crocodile whipping tail!

61
00:07:30.508 --> 00:07:32.550
Confronting elephant!

62
00:07:32.550 --> 00:07:33.550
Hanuman (Monkey) giving ring.

63
00:07:33.550 --> 00:07:35.550
The threatening fight.

64
00:07:35.550 --> 00:07:36.592
The rear kick.

65
00:07:36.592 --> 00:07:38.592
Both elbows attacking...

66
00:07:38.592 --> 00:07:39.592
followed with high knee.

67
00:07:39.592 --> 00:07:41.592
Raising the arms.

68
00:07:41.592 --> 00:07:43.550
Getting high strength.

69
00:07:43.550 --> 00:07:45.550
Cutting through the enemy.

70
00:07:45.550 --> 00:07:47.550
Avoiding danger.

71
00:07:47.550 --> 00:07:49.550
Putting your head down.

72
00:07:49.550 --> 00:07:51.550
Knight throwing an axe.

73
00:07:51.550 --> 00:07:53.550
Wave smashing the shore.

74
00:07:53.550 --> 00:07:55.467
Meet friend. join friend.

75
00:07:56.550 --> 00:07:58.550
Knight catching monkeys.

76
00:07:58.550 --> 00:08:00.467
Breaking the joints.

77
00:08:01.550 --> 00:08:03.550
Snake chasing lizard.

78
00:08:03.550 --> 00:08:05.550
Cliff shaking.

79
00:08:05.550 --> 00:08:07.550
Sticky water.

80
00:08:07.550 --> 00:08:08.508
Throwing the spear.

81
00:08:08.508 --> 00:08:10.508
Breaking the sword.

82
00:08:10.508 --> 00:08:11.508
Raising the body.

83
00:08:11.508 --> 00:08:13.425
Horse replacing bird.

84
00:08:26.592 --> 00:08:28.592
I'll teach you all these styles...

85
00:08:28.592 --> 00:08:32.467
but I forbid you to use them for money.

86
00:08:33.550 --> 00:08:37.550
Do you understand. Bak Tim?

87
00:08:37.550 --> 00:08:39.550
I understand. Pra Kroo.

88
00:08:39.550 --> 00:08:41.467
Good.

89
00:08:48.550 --> 00:08:50.550
He has gone.

90
00:08:50.550 --> 00:08:54.467
You said you understood. Really?

91
00:09:03.550 --> 00:09:05.550
There is a story that...

92
00:09:05.550 --> 00:09:08.550
Pra Kroo learnt this boxing...

93
00:09:08.550 --> 00:09:12.550
from the ancient books.

94
00:09:12.550 --> 00:09:15.550
Then Pra Kroo wanted a challenge.

95
00:09:15.550 --> 00:09:18.550
He went into the boxing ring for money...

96
00:09:18.550 --> 00:09:22.467
and he hit his opponent to death.

97
00:09:23.550 --> 00:09:26.550
He felt very guilty.

98
00:09:26.550 --> 00:09:28.550
so he became a monk.

99
00:09:28.550 --> 00:09:30.467
Thai boxing is very dangerous.

100
00:09:31.550 --> 00:09:35.467
I don't want you to use it. unless
it is absolutely necessary.

101
00:09:36.550 --> 00:09:38.467
Understand?

102
00:09:39.550 --> 00:09:43.467
Or are you still not clear?

103
00:09:44.550 --> 00:09:47.592
Come. fight with me.

104
00:09:47.592 --> 00:09:48.550
Ai Bak. here.

105
00:09:48.550 --> 00:09:50.467
Uncle!
Come on!

106
00:10:25.550 --> 00:10:29.467
Who is there? What are you doing?

107
00:10:38.550 --> 00:10:40.467
Hurry!

108
00:10:50.550 --> 00:10:51.550
Bak Don...

109
00:10:51.550 --> 00:10:55.467
is the one that cut off the head of Ong Bak.

110
00:10:59.550 --> 00:11:03.508
He took all the donation money too. Pra Kroo.

111
00:11:03.508 --> 00:11:07.425
Bak Don! Evil son!

112
00:11:09.508 --> 00:11:12.508
If Pra Ong Bak has no head.

113
00:11:12.508 --> 00:11:16.550
our village will be faced with disaster.

114
00:11:16.550 --> 00:11:18.550
Calm down. calm down!

115
00:11:18.550 --> 00:11:22.592
We must try to get Ong Bak's head back...

116
00:11:22.592 --> 00:11:26.592
to our village before the ceremony day.

117
00:11:26.592 --> 00:11:30.467
Where can we find it. Pra Kroo ?

118
00:11:32.550 --> 00:11:35.550
I will bring Ong Bak back here myself.

119
00:11:35.550 --> 00:11:39.467
Who knows where Bak Don is?

120
00:11:41.550 --> 00:11:45.550
The hopes of the people of Ban Nong Pradoo Sukon...

121
00:11:45.550 --> 00:11:48.550
is in your hands.

122
00:11:48.550 --> 00:11:51.550
In this tube is a holy herbal medicine.

123
00:11:51.550 --> 00:11:53.508
My teacher told me...

124
00:11:53.508 --> 00:11:56.508
it belonged to Kroo Dum.

125
00:11:56.508 --> 00:11:58.467
Keep it with you.

126
00:12:04.550 --> 00:12:06.467
This is the address of Bak Don.

127
00:12:07.550 --> 00:12:11.550
and this is a letter to Bak Hum Lae.

128
00:12:11.550 --> 00:12:15.508
Tim. you must return to our village...

129
00:12:16.550 --> 00:12:18.467
with Ong Bak.

130
00:12:27.550 --> 00:12:31.467
This is the money for your journey.

131
00:12:32.550 --> 00:12:34.467
All my hopes are with you.

132
00:12:37.550 --> 00:12:41.467
My mum gave me this ring before she died.

133
00:12:42.592 --> 00:12:46.467
Warn. please look after grandma.

134
00:13:03.550 --> 00:13:07.425
We've all contributed together...

135
00:13:08.508 --> 00:13:12.467
for the fares.

136
00:13:47.550 --> 00:13:49.467
He's losing.

137
00:13:59.508 --> 00:14:03.508
Hey! What bike you using to race?

138
00:14:03.508 --> 00:14:05.508
Why did you lose so easily like this?

139
00:14:05.508 --> 00:14:07.550
Hey! Why are you speaking that way?

140
00:14:07.550 --> 00:14:09.550
Winning or losing is normal in any bet.

141
00:14:09.550 --> 00:14:11.550
It isn't fair to blame me.

142
00:14:11.550 --> 00:14:14.550
Why did you use a woman to race with me?

143
00:14:14.550 --> 00:14:16.592
Why not?
What's wrong with being a woman?

144
00:14:16.592 --> 00:14:19.292
Ow! You dare race against me!

145
00:14:19.292 --> 00:14:20.692
You cow!

146
00:14:20.792 --> 00:14:23.550
If you rode as fast as your mouth. you'd probably win!

147
00:14:23.550 --> 00:14:25.467
Hey! Hey!

148
00:14:39.550 --> 00:14:41.550
Hey! Why don't you pay me in cash?

149
00:14:41.550 --> 00:14:44.550
You bet me with drugs. didn't you?

150
00:14:44.550 --> 00:14:48.425
You told me it was okay to use drugs instead of cash.

151
00:14:49.508 --> 00:14:51.467
Fine...

152
00:14:58.550 --> 00:15:00.550
I'll give you only 10.000...

153
00:15:00.550 --> 00:15:03.050
after deducting the 10.000 you owe me.

154
00:15:03.050 --> 00:15:05.050
I pay you interest every month.

155
00:15:05.050 --> 00:15:06.550
and the loan isn't due yet...

156
00:15:06.550 --> 00:15:08.550
Can't you give me all the money now?

157
00:15:09.050 --> 00:15:10.950
Do you want it or not?

158
00:15:10.950 --> 00:15:13.967
Fine.  Better than nothing.

159
00:15:21.550 --> 00:15:24.550
Hey! Give me all of that.

160
00:15:24.550 --> 00:15:26.550
What?

161
00:15:26.550 --> 00:15:28.467
Give me that!

162
00:15:29.550 --> 00:15:31.550
You've already got my money.

163
00:15:31.550 --> 00:15:34.592
Can't you give a few tablets to my friends?

164
00:15:34.592 --> 00:15:37.592
You can find this drug anywhere...

165
00:15:37.592 --> 00:15:39.550
you don't have to take mine.

166
00:15:39.550 --> 00:15:41.550
Better not to use my pills anyway.

167
00:15:41.550 --> 00:15:44.550
They're too strong.
Your friends might go into shock.

168
00:15:44.550 --> 00:15:46.550
Believe me.

169
00:15:46.550 --> 00:15:48.467
Huh?

170
00:15:59.550 --> 00:16:01.425
Son of a bitch!

171
00:16:09.508 --> 00:16:13.550
Eh! You're back at last. My money!

172
00:16:13.550 --> 00:16:17.592
Give me my share quickly. Quickly!

173
00:16:17.592 --> 00:16:19.592
Ai Keng caught me.

174
00:16:19.592 --> 00:16:22.592
He knew we bet with fake drugs.
He took all the money back

175
00:16:22.592 --> 00:16:24.592
What? Don't tease me -

176
00:16:24.592 --> 00:16:26.592
it's not funny at all.

177
00:16:26.592 --> 00:16:28.550
Muaylek. look at my face.

178
00:16:28.550 --> 00:16:30.050
Do you think I kicked myself?

179
00:16:30.550 --> 00:16:31.550
Damn!

180
00:16:34.550 --> 00:16:38.550
Oy! Why are you poking me?
I'm still in pain.

181
00:16:38.550 --> 00:16:41.008
Oh well.  How come you got caught?

182
00:16:41.550 --> 00:16:42.550
Forget it!

183
00:16:42.550 --> 00:16:44.050
Do you have 200 baht?

184
00:16:44.550 --> 00:16:47.550
What! You lost all my share and
you're still asking me for my money?

185
00:16:47.550 --> 00:16:49.550
Listen. Muay...

186
00:16:49.550 --> 00:16:52.550
When I won. you took the money.

187
00:16:52.550 --> 00:16:54.508
Now I've lost. so you must share the loss too.

188
00:16:54.508 --> 00:16:57.508
Ow! You're stupid to get caught.

189
00:16:57.508 --> 00:16:59.508
and lose the money in your hands.

190
00:16:59.508 --> 00:17:01.550
So I'm stupid and you're clever!

191
00:17:01.550 --> 00:17:04.550
Ai Keng give me only 3 days.

192
00:17:04.550 --> 00:17:08.550
If I don't pay back his loan he'll
beat the shit out of me!

193
00:17:08.550 --> 00:17:10.508
Ai Hum Lae?

194
00:17:12.592 --> 00:17:14.592
Is it really you. Ai Hum Lae?

195
00:17:14.592 --> 00:17:15.592
Hi.

196
00:17:15.592 --> 00:17:19.050
Uh... Muay. is this your friend?

197
00:17:19.050 --> 00:17:20.550
How could he be my friend?

198
00:17:20.550 --> 00:17:23.550
He is calling you. isn't he?

199
00:17:23.550 --> 00:17:25.550
- Do you know him?
- Yeah!

200
00:17:25.550 --> 00:17:28.550
Remember me? I'm Bak Tim
from Ban Nong Pradoo.

201
00:17:28.550 --> 00:17:30.550
Hey. fool. I don't know you...

202
00:17:30.550 --> 00:17:34.550
Fool! Listen to me. I've just told
you I don't know you!

203
00:17:35.008 --> 00:17:36.550
But I know you. Ai Hum Lae

204
00:17:36.550 --> 00:17:38.550
Hum Lae. Hum what!

205
00:17:38.550 --> 00:17:40.550
What a stupid name! Hum Lae!

206
00:17:40.550 --> 00:17:42.550
Bad luck! I warn you... you're a fool.

207
00:17:42.550 --> 00:17:45.550
Ow! No need to lie! Ai Hum Lae... Oops

208
00:17:45.550 --> 00:17:47.550
Sorry! Slip of my tongue.

209
00:17:47.550 --> 00:17:50.550
Mind your own business.

210
00:17:50.550 --> 00:17:53.550
Get out of my sight! Out!

211
00:17:53.550 --> 00:17:56.550
Okay. You said you were from... Ban? Which?

212
00:17:56.550 --> 00:17:57.550
Ban Nong Pradoo.

213
00:17:57.550 --> 00:17:59.467
That's it. Ban Nong Pradoo.

214
00:18:00.550 --> 00:18:02.550
Okay. I'm leaving.

215
00:18:02.550 --> 00:18:04.550
So you're both from Ban Nong Pradoo.
Can have a good chat!

216
00:18:04.550 --> 00:18:06.592
Very funny! You've made your point!

217
00:18:06.592 --> 00:18:09.508
Go! Go away. but give me the money first.

218
00:18:09.508 --> 00:18:11.467
Here! For your medicine.

219
00:18:12.550 --> 00:18:16.550
I'm going now. Ai Hum Lae...

220
00:18:16.550 --> 00:18:20.550
Listen. peasant!
You should return to your hometown.

221
00:18:20.550 --> 00:18:21.467
Go!

222
00:18:22.550 --> 00:18:25.550
Ai Ham Lae. I have to give you a letter.

223
00:18:25.550 --> 00:18:29.508
I told you I don't know you! Get out!

224
00:18:33.550 --> 00:18:35.550
This is my place.

225
00:18:35.550 --> 00:18:38.550
Don't be angry with me.
Close the door.

226
00:18:38.550 --> 00:18:40.550
Don't let any mosquitos in.

227
00:18:40.550 --> 00:18:44.467
I'm in a bad mood and depressed.

228
00:18:45.550 --> 00:18:47.467
Ai Hum Lae.

229
00:18:48.550 --> 00:18:52.467
Our villagers are in serious trouble...

230
00:18:53.550 --> 00:18:56.550
because Bak Don stole the head of Ong Bak

231
00:18:56.550 --> 00:19:00.550
The Chief sent me here to see you.

232
00:19:00.550 --> 00:19:03.508
so you can help me to find Ong Bak.

233
00:19:03.508 --> 00:19:06.508
I have Bak Don's address.

234
00:19:06.508 --> 00:19:09.508
No need to talk yet.
and put your things down here.

235
00:19:09.508 --> 00:19:10.592
You're better have a wash first.

236
00:19:10.592 --> 00:19:12.592
Go. go now.

237
00:19:12.592 --> 00:19:14.592
Here. here is the washroom.

238
00:19:14.592 --> 00:19:15.592
Go in.

239
00:19:15.592 --> 00:19:17.050
I don't have any other clothing.

240
00:19:17.050 --> 00:19:19.592
Don't worry I'll give you my towel.
Go in. go.

241
00:19:20.050 --> 00:19:21.592
I'll turn on the light for you.

242
00:19:21.592 --> 00:19:24.550
Soap is on your left.
toothbrush on your right.

243
00:19:24.550 --> 00:19:27.550
Mind the slippery floor.

244
00:19:27.550 --> 00:19:29.467
Hello! Muay!

245
00:19:30.550 --> 00:19:32.467
I'll meet you at the stadium...

246
00:19:33.550 --> 00:19:35.467
...the boxing stadium.  Okay.

247
00:20:16.550 --> 00:20:18.550
Are you still taking bets?

248
00:20:18.550 --> 00:20:20.550
Do I have time?

249
00:20:20.550 --> 00:20:22.467
Yes.

250
00:20:23.550 --> 00:20:25.467
Here! All of them!

251
00:20:37.592 --> 00:20:39.467
Do you have the amulet?

252
00:20:41.550 --> 00:20:43.550
The chief changed his mind and didn't want to sell. Boss.

253
00:20:43.550 --> 00:20:46.592
But I have the head of Ong Bak. Boss.

254
00:20:46.592 --> 00:20:49.550
This is the most holy thing in the village...

255
00:20:49.550 --> 00:20:53.467
that they all worship. and the most valuable.

256
00:20:54.550 --> 00:20:57.550
This broken head -

257
00:20:57.550 --> 00:20:59.467
why did you bring it to me?

258
00:21:00.550 --> 00:21:04.508
I'm not interested. Take it away!

259
00:21:04.508 --> 00:21:07.508
My head is hurting enough without...

260
00:21:07.508 --> 00:21:11.467
...you spoiling my mood.

261
00:21:16.550 --> 00:21:19.008
Today. Captain seems to have little to please him.

262
00:21:19.550 --> 00:21:21.592
Look at your fighter. Pearl Harbour.

263
00:21:21.592 --> 00:21:25.050
I think he's losing to Arun. my fighter.
with his Kamikaze technique.

264
00:21:25.050 --> 00:21:26.467
Defeat's certain!

265
00:22:00.508 --> 00:22:03.508
I don't have the money yet -
still trying to get some.

266
00:22:03.508 --> 00:22:07.592
I'm not asking for money.
I can find that myself.

267
00:22:07.592 --> 00:22:10.592
Now you're selling drugs too?

268
00:22:10.992 --> 00:22:12.592
Yes.

269
00:22:17.592 --> 00:22:20.050
My fighter will win the next competition.

270
00:22:20.050 --> 00:22:23.550
If you think you will win.
then why not increase your bet.

271
00:22:23.550 --> 00:22:25.750
Any amount you like. ha ha!

272
00:22:25.750 --> 00:22:27.150
You don't need to preach to me.

273
00:22:27.150 --> 00:22:28.550
you don't really understand me.

274
00:22:28.550 --> 00:22:30.550
Just because of one stinking guy...

275
00:22:30.550 --> 00:22:33.550
you turn yourself into this low-life.

276
00:22:34.050 --> 00:22:36.550
Muay. you're not my mother!

277
00:22:36.550 --> 00:22:40.550
Ever since we lost our parents.
you've become like this.

278
00:22:40.550 --> 00:22:44.425
Yes. a bad person like me.
who has brought you up until now.

279
00:22:44.508 --> 00:22:49.092
From now on. a good person like you
should leave me alone.

280
00:22:55.550 --> 00:22:59.467
Yes. tell me whenever you want it.

281
00:23:10.550 --> 00:23:12.467
Strike. strike.

282
00:23:13.550 --> 00:23:15.467
Knock out.

283
00:23:25.550 --> 00:23:27.467
Get up and hit back.

284
00:23:37.550 --> 00:23:39.467
Yesss...

285
00:23:41.550 --> 00:23:45.550
The next one is coming.

286
00:23:45.550 --> 00:23:48.550
Tell me if you still want to bet.

287
00:23:48.550 --> 00:23:50.467
<i>[laughs]</i>

288
00:23:52.550 --> 00:23:54.467
The winner is... Pearl Harbour.

289
00:23:56.550 --> 00:23:58.508
Damn!

290
00:23:58.508 --> 00:24:00.467
Pearl Habour is Number One!

291
00:24:02.508 --> 00:24:05.550
Two wins two minutes.
Two wins two minutes.

292
00:24:05.550 --> 00:24:06.650
Where are all my things?

293
00:24:06.650 --> 00:24:08.550
What?

294
00:24:08.550 --> 00:24:09.550
My money bag. where is it?

295
00:24:09.550 --> 00:24:11.550
I don't know. I didn't take it.

296
00:24:11.550 --> 00:24:13.467
Him.

297
00:24:18.592 --> 00:24:21.592
Two and one...

298
00:24:21.592 --> 00:24:23.467
Oh! A fresh challenger.

299
00:24:29.550 --> 00:24:33.467
Taking bets now. taking bets now.

300
00:24:36.550 --> 00:24:40.550
Aw... How come that peasant is in the fighting ring?

301
00:24:40.550 --> 00:24:44.467
Yeah... Ai Tim is surely dead.

302
00:24:45.550 --> 00:24:48.508
I'll give you 10 to 1.

303
00:24:48.508 --> 00:24:51.508
But you'd better not dare to bet.

304
00:24:51.508 --> 00:24:55.425
Okay... I'll bet one million.
if you'll dare to accept it.

305
00:24:56.508 --> 00:24:57.508
I accept.

306
00:24:58.050 --> 00:25:00.550
I'm not here to box. I want the money.

307
00:25:00.550 --> 00:25:04.508
Calm down. I'll give you the money later.
Start!

308
00:25:23.550 --> 00:25:27.550
We have a new champion tonight!

309
00:25:27.550 --> 00:25:29.550
What's your name?

310
00:25:29.550 --> 00:25:31.550
Tim from Ban Nong Pradoo.

311
00:25:31.550 --> 00:25:33.467
Tim Pradoo Prew!

312
00:25:41.508 --> 00:25:45.467
Prize for the winner!

313
00:25:49.550 --> 00:25:52.550
I don't want it.
I only want my money bag. there.

314
00:25:52.550 --> 00:25:54.467
What an idiot!

315
00:26:04.550 --> 00:26:08.550
Hey! Hey! Why don't you take the prize
money? Why are you so stupid?

316
00:26:08.550 --> 00:26:10.550
Tell me if you want to fight again.

317
00:26:10.550 --> 00:26:12.550
You have the skill to win.

318
00:26:12.550 --> 00:26:16.550
I can see lots of money. lots and lots.

319
00:26:16.550 --> 00:26:18.550
You ask me to fight for money.

320
00:26:18.550 --> 00:26:20.550
Ai Hum Lae -

321
00:26:20.550 --> 00:26:22.550
why did you steal the villagers' money.
to gamble?

322
00:26:22.550 --> 00:26:24.592
For the investment...

323
00:26:24.592 --> 00:26:28.467
to get enough money to help you find Ong Bak.

324
00:26:29.550 --> 00:26:33.550
- You really want to help me?
- Yes.

325
00:26:33.550 --> 00:26:36.550
This is Don's address.
Could you take me there?

326
00:26:36.550 --> 00:26:38.550
Keep it. I'll take you there later.

327
00:26:38.550 --> 00:26:40.550
Now could you give me some money.

328
00:26:40.550 --> 00:26:42.550
Give me some. for the investment.

329
00:26:42.550 --> 00:26:43.550
When I make a profit. I will pay you back.

330
00:26:43.550 --> 00:26:45.550
and I'll go anywhere you want.

331
00:26:45.550 --> 00:26:48.967
For sure!

332
00:26:52.550 --> 00:26:55.467
Go! Go away! Damn you!

333
00:26:55.467 --> 00:26:58.508
Peasant! Can't talk to you. stupid!

334
00:26:58.508 --> 00:27:00.508
Hey! Where will he sleep tonight?

335
00:27:00.508 --> 00:27:03.550
I don't care! Or he can sleep with you!

336
00:27:03.550 --> 00:27:05.467
You're crazy!

337
00:27:07.550 --> 00:27:10.592
What should I do? Ai Keng will kill me.

338
00:27:10.592 --> 00:27:13.592
Muay! Take these drugs to sell in Yai Lao's den.

339
00:27:13.592 --> 00:27:15.592
When we have enough money.
I'll pay you back.

340
00:27:15.792 --> 00:27:17.592
I'm sure to earn something.
I know this place well.

341
00:27:17.792 --> 00:27:20.550
After the last time.
you still haven't learnt anything.

342
00:27:20.550 --> 00:27:24.550
I told you before.
I don't want to sell drugs.

343
00:27:24.550 --> 00:27:27.550
You have to help me out.
I don't want to get my ass kicked again.

344
00:27:28.150 --> 00:27:29.450
OK?

345
00:27:29.650 --> 00:27:33.550
Yeah. Yeah... I'll try.
but it'll have to be tomorrow.

346
00:27:33.550 --> 00:27:37.467
Okay... I feel so much better now.

347
00:27:43.508 --> 00:27:45.508
You don't have to look so happy.

348
00:27:45.508 --> 00:27:49.508
From the takings.
you'll get 30. but I'll get 70.

349
00:27:49.508 --> 00:27:51.150
Muay! 50/50!

350
00:27:51.250 --> 00:27:52.492
70/30!

351
00:27:52.492 --> 00:27:53.550
50/50!

352
00:27:53.550 --> 00:27:54.550
70/30!

353
00:28:27.550 --> 00:28:30.550
The money you asked for
starting your business in Bangkok

354
00:28:30.550 --> 00:28:32.550
I don't have it...

355
00:28:32.550 --> 00:28:36.550
because we had a very dry season.

356
00:28:36.550 --> 00:28:38.550
and Ong Bak's head was stolen by Ai Don.

357
00:28:38.550 --> 00:28:42.550
Dad wishes that you will help Bak Tim
to find and return Ong Bak to us...

358
00:28:42.550 --> 00:28:44.550
and save us from disaster.

359
00:28:44.550 --> 00:28:46.467
What nonsense!

360
00:29:14.550 --> 00:29:18.467
The well is dry... Where are
we going to find drinking water?

361
00:29:23.550 --> 00:29:27.467
I pray to have Ong Bak back with us soon. please.

362
00:29:34.508 --> 00:29:38.467
Ai Rung. are you alone?

363
00:29:39.550 --> 00:29:41.467
Ai Piew. are you betting?

364
00:29:42.550 --> 00:29:44.550
Brother I'm here.

365
00:29:44.550 --> 00:29:46.550
Damn Ai Yod.
Where have you been for months?

366
00:29:46.550 --> 00:29:48.508
I had to see my friends.

367
00:29:48.508 --> 00:29:50.508
You are fully aware that I'm short of staff.

368
00:29:50.508 --> 00:29:52.508
You assist me first. hurry.

369
00:29:52.508 --> 00:29:54.508
Not now. I have to meet a friend.

370
00:29:54.508 --> 00:29:56.508
Don't make excuses. you help me now.

371
00:29:56.508 --> 00:29:57.508
Not today. some other day.

372
00:29:57.508 --> 00:29:59.550
No. now. quickly!

373
00:30:00.550 --> 00:30:02.508
Take it.

374
00:30:04.592 --> 00:30:06.508
Go away. you deal cards badly.

375
00:30:08.592 --> 00:30:10.592
Put down your bets now.

376
00:30:10.592 --> 00:30:14.467
At your age you should stay at home.
looking after your children

377
00:30:16.550 --> 00:30:18.550
What are you looking at? Get out!

378
00:30:18.550 --> 00:30:20.550
Go to that desk...

379
00:30:20.550 --> 00:30:22.550
and change your hair colour too.

380
00:30:22.550 --> 00:30:26.467
The colour that suits me.
and you have to copy.

381
00:30:28.550 --> 00:30:30.467
Put down your bets. to lose. to lose.

382
00:30:31.550 --> 00:30:34.550
Betting and losing is not my fault.

383
00:30:34.550 --> 00:30:36.550
Turn the cards.
19 and 19 both hands.

384
00:30:40.508 --> 00:30:42.508
Pay up.

385
00:30:42.508 --> 00:30:44.425
More bets down. bet. bet.

386
00:30:46.550 --> 00:30:47.550
Here's mine.

387
00:30:47.550 --> 00:30:48.550
Do you have money?

388
00:30:48.550 --> 00:30:50.550
Here it is - 3.000 real money.

389
00:30:50.550 --> 00:30:53.550
You want to play? You will lose...

390
00:30:53.550 --> 00:30:55.550
all your money and your belongings.

391
00:30:55.550 --> 00:30:59.592
I bet 200.
Okay. 200.

392
00:30:59.592 --> 00:31:01.467
No card swapping.

393
00:31:02.592 --> 00:31:04.467
Oh! 18 points.

394
00:31:05.350 --> 00:31:07.450
Pay up.

395
00:31:07.649 --> 00:31:12.449
Wait... I have 19.  I win.

396
00:31:15.250 --> 00:31:17.467
This is 400.

397
00:31:22.550 --> 00:31:26.550
- Ai has only 6 points. 1 card.
- Mine is 9.

398
00:31:29.550 --> 00:31:34.092
- 8 points 3 cards.
- 9 points!

399
00:31:34.550 --> 00:31:36.550
What sort of cards are these?

400
00:31:38.550 --> 00:31:40.467
She's lucky.

401
00:31:41.550 --> 00:31:46.550
- It's luck. good luck.
- 9 points!

402
00:31:48.550 --> 00:31:50.550
- 8 points again.
- 9 points again!

403
00:31:51.550 --> 00:31:55.467
Damn cards. take it.

404
00:31:57.550 --> 00:31:59.550
8 points again.

405
00:31:59.550 --> 00:32:03.467
Got you. pay up!

406
00:32:04.550 --> 00:32:07.550
- Damn! 8 points again.
- 9 to beat you!

407
00:32:09.550 --> 00:32:12.592
These cards are impossible.

408
00:32:12.592 --> 00:32:15.592
I must check if she is cheating!

409
00:32:18.550 --> 00:32:21.550
She got all 9 points for 15 games.
Took most of my money.

410
00:32:21.550 --> 00:32:23.467
Why are you paying her?

411
00:32:24.550 --> 00:32:28.550
I want to see if you will get 9 again.

412
00:32:28.550 --> 00:32:30.467
You're cheating me. bitch!

413
00:32:31.550 --> 00:32:35.467
I know I got 8 without turning the cards.

414
00:32:36.550 --> 00:32:38.550
Points? If it's 9...

415
00:32:38.550 --> 00:32:40.467
I'm certain that you cheat.

416
00:32:43.508 --> 00:32:46.508
Look! Loser! She got 4 points.

417
00:32:46.508 --> 00:32:47.508
I don't believe it.

418
00:32:48.508 --> 00:32:51.508
She must be hiding some cards...
I want to search her!

419
00:32:51.508 --> 00:32:53.508
Wait... Calm down!

420
00:32:54.508 --> 00:32:56.592
You should search her.

421
00:32:56.592 --> 00:32:57.592
Hey! Did you hide any cards?

422
00:32:57.592 --> 00:32:59.592
- No. I didn't.
- Let's see.

423
00:32:59.592 --> 00:33:01.592
There are none. I told you.

424
00:33:01.592 --> 00:33:02.592
Any hidden in your bag?

425
00:33:02.592 --> 00:33:03.592
Let me check her myself.

426
00:33:03.592 --> 00:33:04.592
Don't trouble yourself.

427
00:33:04.592 --> 00:33:06.550
Come here.
Okay. you can go.

428
00:33:06.550 --> 00:33:07.592
You've got to search her everywhere.

429
00:33:07.592 --> 00:33:09.550
All done. searched everywhere.
You can go. go now.

430
00:33:09.550 --> 00:33:13.550
Don't come back here again. bitch!

431
00:33:13.550 --> 00:33:17.550
Winning every game like that
is bad for my place.

432
00:33:17.550 --> 00:33:19.550
Let's continue. we can beat these people.

433
00:33:19.550 --> 00:33:21.550
There's no point. they're all broke.
Broke! Broke!

434
00:33:21.550 --> 00:33:23.550
She took all their money. they have nothing left.

435
00:33:23.550 --> 00:33:25.008
Don't you have a go at me.

436
00:33:25.008 --> 00:33:27.550
Total 8.000. I give your 3.000 back.

437
00:33:27.550 --> 00:33:29.550
Why is it only 3.000?

438
00:33:29.550 --> 00:33:31.550
You won't need so much anyway.

439
00:33:31.550 --> 00:33:33.508
What? No profit for me at all?

440
00:33:33.508 --> 00:33:35.508
Ugh... You take this money first.

441
00:33:35.508 --> 00:33:36.508
Don't spend too much.

442
00:33:36.508 --> 00:33:37.508
Give me another 1.000.

443
00:33:37.508 --> 00:33:39.550
3.000 is enough for you.

444
00:33:39.550 --> 00:33:41.550
This will barely cover my college fees.

445
00:33:41.550 --> 00:33:44.550
Hey! You seem to have a lot of money...

446
00:33:44.550 --> 00:33:46.467
It's that guy...

447
00:33:47.550 --> 00:33:49.550
Lend me your money.

448
00:33:49.550 --> 00:33:51.550
- This is my money!
- Er... I'll pay you back.

449
00:33:51.550 --> 00:33:52.550
I'll pay you back.

450
00:33:52.550 --> 00:33:56.592
Hi! I was on my way to pay you.
but you beat me to it. Here!

451
00:33:56.592 --> 00:33:57.592
That is my money.

452
00:33:57.592 --> 00:33:59.467
What?

453
00:34:01.550 --> 00:34:04.550
8.000 - I'll give you the rest later.

454
00:34:04.550 --> 00:34:07.550
Don't look at me so menacingly.

455
00:34:07.550 --> 00:34:09.550
I'm not bothered too much
about the rest of the money.

456
00:34:09.550 --> 00:34:13.467
but when you two try to cheat me.
I can't forget!

457
00:34:15.550 --> 00:34:19.467
Hold him! Beat him!
No. I won't fight you.

458
00:34:21.550 --> 00:34:23.467
Ai Tim!   Ai Tim!

459
00:34:25.550 --> 00:34:28.467
I won't fight. I won't fight.
Help! Help!

460
00:34:31.550 --> 00:34:34.550
You cheated me. here!

461
00:34:45.550 --> 00:34:46.550
You want trouble?

462
00:34:46.550 --> 00:34:48.467
Here's some!

463
00:34:58.550 --> 00:35:00.467
We'll see you again later!

464
00:35:03.550 --> 00:35:05.550
I have to thank you. Ai Tim.

465
00:35:05.550 --> 00:35:09.508
And I will help you to find Ong Bak

466
00:35:10.592 --> 00:35:14.550
Could you fight one more time?

467
00:35:14.550 --> 00:35:16.550
Wait... Listen to me first.

468
00:35:16.550 --> 00:35:19.550
You saw just a minute ago. they beat me up.

469
00:35:19.550 --> 00:35:21.550
If I don't pay them. they will kill me.

470
00:35:21.550 --> 00:35:22.550
Can you help me?

471
00:35:22.550 --> 00:35:24.550
One last fight for me.

472
00:35:25.550 --> 00:35:28.550
Okay. fine. It doesn't matter anyway.
Stupid peasant!

473
00:35:28.550 --> 00:35:32.467
Stupid village. stupid villagers!
Relying on just one boxer...

474
00:35:32.550 --> 00:35:35.750
to find and return Ong Bak
to their village. Are you crazy?

475
00:35:35.750 --> 00:35:39.508
If Ong Bak is so powerful.
why let a thief cut his head off?

476
00:35:39.508 --> 00:35:42.425
It's only made from pieces of stone and earth!

477
00:35:45.467 --> 00:35:47.508
You hit me! Why'd you hit me?

478
00:35:47.508 --> 00:35:49.550
You're from the same village.
Don't kill each other.

479
00:35:49.550 --> 00:35:50.550
He punched me!

480
00:35:50.550 --> 00:35:54.508
Never mind that! There! The people
you want to kill are over there!

481
00:35:55.592 --> 00:35:59.050
Ai Peng! Haven't you had enough?

482
00:35:59.050 --> 00:36:02.592
You want a kick to send you to sleep?

483
00:36:04.550 --> 00:36:08.550
Umm... You have too many.

484
00:36:08.550 --> 00:36:12.467
Ai Yod. You know very well what to do.

485
00:36:14.550 --> 00:36:18.467
Muay. You know what to do.

486
00:36:19.550 --> 00:36:23.467
Every man for himself.

487
00:36:26.550 --> 00:36:28.508
Don't leave me!

488
00:36:28.508 --> 00:36:30.425
After them!

489
00:36:42.550 --> 00:36:46.467
Follow them.
I'll go to block the other way.

490
00:36:55.550 --> 00:36:57.550
You!  I'm going!

491
00:37:21.550 --> 00:37:23.467
Look out. look out!

492
00:37:36.550 --> 00:37:38.467
Oh! How did he get over that?

493
00:37:45.508 --> 00:37:49.467
Ooh! Is my ass okay?
I don't know how I made that.

494
00:38:36.508 --> 00:38:38.508
Let me borrow the cleaver. quick.

495
00:38:38.508 --> 00:38:42.467
Come near me and I will slaughter you.

496
00:38:55.592 --> 00:38:59.467
Knives! Knives!
Big ones. small ones for sale.

497
00:39:35.550 --> 00:39:37.467
'Chilli Powder'

498
00:39:58.550 --> 00:40:00.467
Get him! Kill him!

499
00:41:26.550 --> 00:41:29.508
Ai Tim! Help me!

500
00:41:29.508 --> 00:41:31.508
I won't help.
You have to fight them yourself.

501
00:41:31.508 --> 00:41:35.508
Ai Don! Yes! I know his address!
I'll take you!

502
00:41:35.508 --> 00:41:39.467
Ai Tim! I know where Ai Don is.

503
00:42:02.550 --> 00:42:06.467
Who's next!

504
00:42:07.550 --> 00:42:09.550
I used to see Ai Don hanging
around here. selling drugs.

505
00:42:09.550 --> 00:42:13.550
Ask Muay. if you don't believe me...

506
00:42:13.550 --> 00:42:17.425
But today...

507
00:42:24.550 --> 00:42:28.467
That boy is here. Boss.

508
00:42:32.050 --> 00:42:36.050
Bring him here to fight until the stakes are high.

509
00:42:36.050 --> 00:42:38.150
then I will get rid of him.

510
00:42:38.650 --> 00:42:42.067
Depends on how brave you are to take a bet?

511
00:42:48.550 --> 00:42:50.467
Hey! You! Aw!

512
00:42:53.550 --> 00:42:55.467
You maniac!

513
00:43:01.550 --> 00:43:05.508
Champion! New champion!
Tim Pradoo Prew !

514
00:43:09.550 --> 00:43:11.550
Come on! Come and fight me!
Come on!

515
00:43:11.550 --> 00:43:15.550
What are you waiting for?
Let's go. I'm here! Come on!

516
00:43:15.550 --> 00:43:19.467
What?  You're scared?  Let's go!
Come on.  Let's go!

517
00:43:21.050 --> 00:43:22.550
What's happening. Yod?

518
00:43:22.550 --> 00:43:25.050
Ai Big Bear is challenging Ai Tim to a fight.

519
00:43:26.050 --> 00:43:29.550
Come on! Thai boxing's good on stage.
You should try freestyle!

520
00:43:29.550 --> 00:43:33.508
You won't beat me.
Thai people are not strong enough!

521
00:43:33.508 --> 00:43:36.508
That's why Thai women come
to my country to become hookers!

522
00:43:36.508 --> 00:43:40.467
Come on! I'll show you.

523
00:43:59.550 --> 00:44:03.467
Come on! I'll fight you!
I'll teach you about Thai boxing! Come on!

524
00:44:07.550 --> 00:44:09.467
Fuck you!

525
00:44:22.550 --> 00:44:26.425
Come on! You want to fight me now. Fight me!

526
00:44:31.550 --> 00:44:33.550
Have you seen Bak Don?

527
00:44:33.550 --> 00:44:35.592
No. but I've seen a Thai man being beaten.

528
00:44:35.592 --> 00:44:37.467
You're a coward.

529
00:44:42.550 --> 00:44:44.508
Come on!

530
00:44:47.592 --> 00:44:51.467
Are you going to help him?
Without help he'll die.

531
00:44:52.550 --> 00:44:54.467
Come on! Come on!

532
00:44:55.550 --> 00:44:58.467
Ai Tim!
Come on!

533
00:45:01.550 --> 00:45:05.008
If I knew you were like this.
I wouldn't have helped you find Ong Bak.

534
00:45:05.008 --> 00:45:09.467
Hey! You can do that later.
But you have to help him first.

535
00:45:15.550 --> 00:45:17.467
I'll kill him.

536
00:45:18.550 --> 00:45:20.467
No!

537
00:45:40.508 --> 00:45:44.467
Next fight! Big Ben and Tim Pradoo Prew.

538
00:45:50.050 --> 00:45:53.550
Lay down your stakes!
Lay down your stakes now!

539
00:45:53.550 --> 00:45:55.467
Lay down your stakes... quickly.

540
00:45:55.550 --> 00:45:58.592
I'll give you 2 to 1. want to bet?

541
00:45:58.592 --> 00:46:01.592
Okay... Put me down for three million.

542
00:46:02.592 --> 00:46:03.550
Begin!

543
00:46:03.550 --> 00:46:05.467
Fight me now! Come on!

544
00:46:06.550 --> 00:46:10.050
Fuck Muay Thai!

545
00:46:12.550 --> 00:46:14.467
Attacking Enemy.

546
00:46:25.550 --> 00:46:27.425
Hanuman (monkey) crosses the city.

547
00:46:30.508 --> 00:46:34.508
If my man wins.
I want to collect the money.

548
00:46:34.508 --> 00:46:36.050
Okay. I know!

549
00:46:36.050 --> 00:46:37.050
Thanks.

550
00:47:19.050 --> 00:47:22.508
Ai Tim! Ai Tim's the best!

551
00:47:23.050 --> 00:47:27.467
I think you've had enough. No chance
to win your money back today.

552
00:48:10.550 --> 00:48:17.008
The next fight!
Tim Pradoo Prew and Toshiro!

553
00:48:42.550 --> 00:48:46.550
Well done! Well done! The best!

554
00:48:46.550 --> 00:48:50.592
- Muay. give me that.
- No.
- Half then.

555
00:48:50.592 --> 00:48:54.508
- I don't have to.
- Trust me.

556
00:50:33.550 --> 00:50:37.592
Do you have any real contenders?

557
00:50:37.592 --> 00:50:39.550
Yes. but do you dare?

558
00:50:39.550 --> 00:50:41.425
Oh! No problem!

559
00:50:50.550 --> 00:50:54.467
Retreat!  Mother of God!

560
00:52:59.008 --> 00:53:01.550
Too much for you? Give up?

561
00:53:04.550 --> 00:53:07.050
Ay! Let go of me!

562
00:53:13.550 --> 00:53:15.550
Ay! Let me go!

563
00:53:52.550 --> 00:53:54.592
You've disappointed me.

564
00:54:23.508 --> 00:54:33.050
Good! The best! I told you Muay!
I told you to bet on him! We're rich! Rich!!

565
00:55:24.650 --> 00:55:27.550
Muay! Pick up the coins!

566
00:55:27.550 --> 00:55:32.050
Enough for today!
You won't win your money back.

567
00:55:36.050 --> 00:55:39.842
Ai Tim! You're so good. we have
a great opportunity to get rich now.

568
00:55:39.842 --> 00:55:41.842
Brilliant!

569
00:55:42.758 --> 00:55:43.842
Ai Don!

570
00:55:46.758 --> 00:55:48.758
Follow them!

571
00:55:49.542 --> 00:55:50.958
Music!

572
00:55:51.358 --> 00:55:53.033
Get them!

573
00:55:54.958 --> 00:55:57.833
Quick! Let's go!

574
00:56:00.958 --> 00:56:02.833
Ai Don!

575
00:56:07.000 --> 00:56:08.833
Follow them!

576
00:56:10.000 --> 00:56:11.958
This week I have to see customers.

577
00:56:11.958 --> 00:56:13.958
I want you to get things ready.

578
00:56:14.258 --> 00:56:17.000
Tell me first if there is a problem.

579
00:56:17.000 --> 00:56:18.958
Yes Boss.

580
00:56:18.958 --> 00:56:21.083
I want you to report everything.

581
00:56:23.042 --> 00:56:26.042
Ai Hum Lae!
Where will we find Ai Bak Don?

582
00:56:26.542 --> 00:56:28.542
You eat your food first. Eat!

583
00:56:28.958 --> 00:56:29.958
Don't worry.

584
00:56:29.958 --> 00:56:33.917
I'll find him! At the rice mill.
everyone knows him well.

585
00:56:33.917 --> 00:56:35.917
Eat!

586
00:56:35.917 --> 00:56:38.917
Muay. tomorrow you'll go with me.

587
00:56:38.917 --> 00:56:41.917
There might be a chance to get some money.

588
00:56:41.917 --> 00:56:43.917
I can't. Exams tomorrow.

589
00:56:43.917 --> 00:56:45.958
Exams! I've never seen you attend class.

590
00:56:45.958 --> 00:56:49.875
How can you pass? You have something
special going on with the teacher?

591
00:56:50.542 --> 00:56:53.000
- What!
- I'm joking. I'm joking...

592
00:56:53.000 --> 00:56:56.833
You're a good student. you're smart...
Eat...

593
00:57:01.083 --> 00:57:03.758
Thanks a lot for helping me find Ong Bak.

594
00:57:03.958 --> 00:57:05.133
Don't thank me.

595
00:57:05.958 --> 00:57:08.917
Ai Yod. you own me 3 months rent.

596
00:57:08.917 --> 00:57:10.958
What are you going to do?

597
00:57:11.042 --> 00:57:13.158
Um... Give me 3 days.

598
00:57:13.758 --> 00:57:15.958
I'll pay you. This time for sure.

599
00:57:15.958 --> 00:57:17.958
You said 'sure' too many times already.

600
00:57:17.958 --> 00:57:20.958
I want money today...
otherwise you're out!

601
00:57:21.958 --> 00:57:22.958
Will you accept this ring instead?

602
00:57:23.917 --> 00:57:24.917
Okay...

603
00:57:24.917 --> 00:57:27.917
You must pay the rent within 7 days.

604
00:57:28.617 --> 00:57:30.317
If you have no money again.

605
00:57:30.317 --> 00:57:33.833
I'll kick you out. understand?

606
00:58:02.542 --> 00:58:05.958
Son. I want you to return home with Bak Tim.

607
00:58:05.958 --> 00:58:07.958
Don't worry if you don't have enough money.

608
00:58:07.958 --> 00:58:10.958
I don't mind if you don't want to become a monk.

609
00:58:10.958 --> 00:58:14.917
I only want you to visit us.

610
00:58:14.917 --> 00:58:16.833
I miss you. son.

611
00:59:05.000 --> 00:59:08.833
What's the matter? Am I not
as good as your ex-husband?

612
00:59:12.542 --> 00:59:13.833
You spoiled my mood.

613
00:59:17.333 --> 00:59:19.250
Don!

614
00:59:19.958 --> 00:59:21.833
I don't want to sell drugs any more.

615
00:59:24.500 --> 00:59:25.833
Why?

616
00:59:33.542 --> 00:59:35.542
I want to stop.

617
00:59:42.583 --> 00:59:44.458
You want to stop?

618
00:59:47.458 --> 00:59:50.875
Really want to stop?
Come here!

619
00:59:52.700 --> 00:59:55.958
You think you can stop that easily.

620
00:59:55.958 --> 00:59:59.833
You think you can but you can't!

621
01:00:24.917 --> 01:00:26.792
Who...?

622
01:00:35.958 --> 01:00:37.875
Huh! Ai Don.

623
01:00:45.542 --> 01:00:48.933
Pi Ngek. Pi Ngek. Pi Ngek. Pi Ngek...

624
01:00:49.542 --> 01:00:51.442
- Where is Ong Bak?
- I don't know.

625
01:00:51.858 --> 01:00:54.558
- You brought it here!
- I don't know.

626
01:00:55.958 --> 01:00:57.458
Ai Tim!

627
01:00:57.458 --> 01:00:59.333
Get off me!

628
01:01:02.958 --> 01:01:04.833
Pi Ngek!

629
01:01:11.958 --> 01:01:15.833
Get out of here quickly!

630
01:01:18.958 --> 01:01:20.833
Go. Go.

631
01:01:22.958 --> 01:01:26.042
Call an ambulance for Room 212.
She's dying. Urgent!

632
01:01:37.917 --> 01:01:41.833
Ai Tim! Over here! Get in the Tuk Tuk!

633
01:01:42.958 --> 01:01:44.833
Hurry up!

634
01:01:45.958 --> 01:01:47.533
You're dead!

635
01:02:45.000 --> 01:02:46.833
Keep following me!

636
01:03:05.958 --> 01:03:07.833
- Come on!
- You're dead!

637
01:03:20.000 --> 01:03:21.833
Huh! Ai Tim.

638
01:03:26.958 --> 01:03:30.875
Ai Tim! Brake! Brake! Brake quickly!

639
01:03:33.958 --> 01:03:35.875
Oh Bhudda! Oh!

640
01:03:50.958 --> 01:03:52.958
Spread them out.

641
01:04:57.958 --> 01:04:59.833
Oh! Damn!

642
01:05:14.958 --> 01:05:16.992
Get out!

643
01:05:25.917 --> 01:05:27.000
You're dead!

644
01:06:21.958 --> 01:06:25.958
Remember. search every
square metre. Don't miss anything.

645
01:06:25.958 --> 01:06:29.875
Most importantly. do not let
any strangers in. Understand?

646
01:06:30.958 --> 01:06:32.833
Damn them! They keep chasing after me.

647
01:08:32.800 --> 01:08:34.575
Get in.

648
01:08:38.042 --> 01:08:40.833
Today the Police and
National Heritage have found...

649
01:08:40.958 --> 01:08:44.958
numerous Buddha statues and relics
on the Chao Praya riverbank.

650
01:08:44.958 --> 01:08:47.958
This finding of priceless objects
is very significant.

651
01:08:47.958 --> 01:08:51.833
Because every piece is a national treasure.

652
01:08:53.958 --> 01:08:58.042
National Heritage is making a catalogue
for protective conservation.

653
01:08:58.042 --> 01:09:02.792
We will report any further
developments on this story.

654
01:09:12.958 --> 01:09:16.958
I told you not to cause trouble.

655
01:09:16.958 --> 01:09:20.833
I didn't. They are looking for Ong Bak.

656
01:09:21.958 --> 01:09:23.833
What's Ong Bak?

657
01:09:24.958 --> 01:09:27.158
The head of the Buddha Statue that I brought to you.

658
01:09:27.558 --> 01:09:30.958
Why does this man cause me so much trouble?

659
01:09:30.958 --> 01:09:32.958
I lost my betting money.

660
01:09:32.958 --> 01:09:34.958
and my entire relics collection...

661
01:09:34.958 --> 01:09:38.042
all because of one peasant.

662
01:09:47.658 --> 01:09:51.175
I'm sorry. I'm afraid I can't save her.

663
01:09:55.900 --> 01:09:59.033
Pi Ngek? Pi Ngek! Pi Ngek!

664
01:10:00.858 --> 01:10:03.958
Pi Ngek. don't leave me!

665
01:10:04.758 --> 01:10:06.233
Who is she?

666
01:10:07.458 --> 01:10:09.258
Muay's big sister.

667
01:10:10.858 --> 01:10:14.133
You can't leave me!
I have nobody!

668
01:10:19.217 --> 01:10:22.792
Muay... Muay...

669
01:10:26.417 --> 01:10:28.933
Ngek asked me to give this to you...

670
01:10:30.958 --> 01:10:32.958
<i>For Muay's College Fees</i>

671
01:10:33.558 --> 01:10:36.475
I don't want it. don't want it!

672
01:10:38.600 --> 01:10:42.700
I want you! I have nobody else!

673
01:10:42.700 --> 01:10:46.633
You can't leave me! I have no one else!

674
01:10:47.558 --> 01:10:49.558
Don't be so sad. Muay.

675
01:10:49.558 --> 01:10:51.733
Birth and death are facts of life.

676
01:10:52.558 --> 01:10:54.558
I won't leave you.

677
01:10:55.183 --> 01:10:58.558
What's this? What?

678
01:10:58.558 --> 01:11:00.558
Where are you taking me?

679
01:11:00.558 --> 01:11:04.433
Let's go. go quickly.
Go. go!

680
01:11:13.517 --> 01:11:16.517
Do you know who I am?

681
01:11:16.517 --> 01:11:18.433
How dare you attack my property!

682
01:11:19.558 --> 01:11:23.558
I don't know. It's between Ai Tim and Ai Don.

683
01:11:23.558 --> 01:11:25.475
Really. I don't know.

684
01:11:38.858 --> 01:11:43.433
I know that you are looking for this head.

685
01:11:44.658 --> 01:11:48.433
Do you really want it?

686
01:11:49.358 --> 01:11:53.433
If you want it. I've got a game for you to play.

687
01:12:00.017 --> 01:12:02.558
I saw Ong Bak with my own eyes.

688
01:12:03.058 --> 01:12:05.258
If you agree to fight for him.

689
01:12:05.258 --> 01:12:09.433
he'll give you Ong Bak and release Muay.

690
01:12:09.800 --> 01:12:14.133
What are you going to do?
Tell me.

691
01:12:16.658 --> 01:12:19.733
I will do anything...

692
01:12:20.158 --> 01:12:23.317
to bring Ong Bak back to Ban Nong Pradoo.

693
01:12:24.517 --> 01:12:27.433
I'd even sacrifice my life.

694
01:12:45.283 --> 01:12:48.033
Why do you call me away from the frontier?

695
01:12:50.242 --> 01:12:57.833
To warn you to stay away from political
issues. and I want you to make a bet.

696
01:12:58.833 --> 01:13:02.833
Oho. you want to revenge that
country boxer to death!

697
01:13:03.583 --> 01:13:05.833
How much you want to bet? It's your call.

698
01:13:07.542 --> 01:13:09.542
You don't call the shots anymore!

699
01:14:03.917 --> 01:14:08.792
<i>On the East corner is the Thai Boxer.
He's a newcomer here...</i>

700
01:14:11.958 --> 01:14:17.833
<i>The Burmese Boxer is on the West
corner. He's one of the best...</i>

701
01:14:19.958 --> 01:14:25.833
<i>Now the fight has begun...</i>

702
01:16:10.042 --> 01:16:14.542
Ai Tim!  Ai Tim! Are you okay?
Enough!

703
01:16:54.042 --> 01:16:56.792
Hey! If you want Ong Bak. follow me.

704
01:17:26.000 --> 01:17:31.000
You're crooks too. Tim lost
the fight so I could win the bet.

705
01:17:41.042 --> 01:17:42.042
Huh! This is Pra!

706
01:17:43.042 --> 01:17:47.042
It's just the head of some worthless
statue that you're trying to get.

707
01:17:48.083 --> 01:17:52.667
I'm not interested in the head.
I just want you to box for me.

708
01:17:53.042 --> 01:17:59.042
Don't dare challenge me because
I can make you live or die.

709
01:18:01.250 --> 01:18:04.042
Damn you! You betrayed us!

710
01:18:05.042 --> 01:18:08.042
Ai Tim lost the fight for you.
why don't you return the head to him?

711
01:18:08.542 --> 01:18:10.667
Son of a bitch!

712
01:18:15.542 --> 01:18:19.667
Calm down.
Finish them after I'm gone.

713
01:18:21.000 --> 01:18:28.500
You got hurt but I got the money.
Remember that I ordered this.

714
01:18:29.667 --> 01:18:32.667
Get rid of them.
I can't help if they don't listen.

715
01:18:49.042 --> 01:18:50.500
Hey! Kill them.

716
01:19:02.042 --> 01:19:03.042
Pi Yod!

717
01:19:05.042 --> 01:19:08.000
Damn! I told him not to make noise.

718
01:19:22.042 --> 01:19:25.042
Hey! Do it quickly!
The police might be here soon!

719
01:19:33.542 --> 01:19:35.667
Hey! Over there!

720
01:21:26.792 --> 01:21:28.667
Where is Ong Bak?

721
01:21:44.042 --> 01:21:49.667
- Hey! I'll go with you.
- No. I can't let anyone die for Ong Bak.

722
01:21:50.042 --> 01:21:52.625
Except me. Only me.

723
01:21:58.542 --> 01:22:01.667
Ai Tim. Ai Tim...

724
01:22:04.000 --> 01:22:06.000
Let me help you.

725
01:22:08.583 --> 01:22:13.333
I don't want to be like this.
I apologize.

726
01:22:13.583 --> 01:22:16.708
Let me do one good deed
for Ban Nong Pradoo!

727
01:22:18.042 --> 01:22:21.542
At least... Let me start the bike for you.

728
01:22:24.167 --> 01:22:29.042
I. Bak Hum Lae. from Ban Nong Pradoo!

729
01:22:40.042 --> 01:22:45.708
Don told me there is a secret cave
behind the next mountain.

730
01:26:24.500 --> 01:26:26.500
Still not dead!

731
01:26:34.083 --> 01:26:37.542
You want Ong Bak? You have to
exchange it for your life.

732
01:26:38.042 --> 01:26:40.042
We're cutting the biggest head.

733
01:28:18.292 --> 01:28:22.833
Ai Tim!  Ai Tim.....Ai Ti...

734
01:29:35.042 --> 01:29:38.042
Ai Ham Lae!  Are you okay?

735
01:29:44.042 --> 01:29:48.042
Go and get Ong Bak. Go!

736
01:29:49.542 --> 01:29:51.542
Don't worry about me.
Go and get Ong Bak.

737
01:29:51.958 --> 01:29:53.000
Go!

738
01:30:56.500 --> 01:31:03.042
Hey! Where are you running to?
Continue working! Cut the head off!

739
01:31:11.500 --> 01:31:15.042
Be careful!
Last time I told him to lose.

740
01:32:24.542 --> 01:32:29.667
The head is off now boss.
Good. pull it off.

741
01:34:21.500 --> 01:34:23.625
Die..e..e...

742
01:36:11.083 --> 01:36:16.667
You want this head!
I want to see if it's unbreakable.

743
01:37:37.583 --> 01:37:38.583
Ai Hum Lae!

744
01:37:40.542 --> 01:37:43.667
Ai Hum Lae... Are you hurt?

745
01:37:46.250 --> 01:37:53.000
Take... take... Ong Bak
back to our... our village.

746
01:37:55.000 --> 01:37:57.667
Ai Pi Yod!  Ai Pi Yod!
What's happenning?

747
01:38:01.000 --> 01:38:02.208
Ai Hum Lae.

748
01:38:02.208 --> 01:38:17.583
Muay... finish... your studying
and find... a good job...

749
01:38:22.042 --> 01:38:32.042
Bak Tim... Tell my dad...
I can't... become a monk...

750
01:38:32.042 --> 01:38:37.542
Huh! Don't talk like that! Let's go to
the hospital and you'll be fine. Pi Yod.

751
01:38:37.542 --> 01:38:41.958
Ai Hum Lae.
Ai Pi Yod. Ai Pi Yod. Hey!

752
01:38:43.042 --> 01:38:48.708
You can't die! You promised
not to leave me. you can't die.

753
01:38:48.708 --> 01:38:54.708
You can't do this! You can't
lie to me. you cannot lie to me!

754
01:38:55.042 --> 01:39:00.042
Do you understand! You promised me!
I have nobody else! I have nobody else!

755
01:39:00.042 --> 01:39:06.333
Wake up now! Don't do this to me.
you can't. can't. Understand!

756
01:39:06.333 --> 01:39:12.667
Wake up now! Ai Pi Yod. you can't die.
You have to keep your promise!

757
01:41:03.668 --> 01:41:06.668
<i>English subtitles fixed by GUiLe ;-)</i>
